      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear u, but saying there is \"no credible legal basis\" sounds pretty definitive. aren't there some scholars or legal experts who argue that UNCLOS might not fully account for historical rights that predate the treaty? it seems like a pretty complex legal debate rather than just one side being wrong.",
